articles.author: Yuliya Talmazan, Reuters
articles.title: E.U. makes historic show of support for Ukraine after U.S. budget deal snub - NBC News
articles.description: All 27 European Union foreign ministers descended on Kyiv on Monday in a historic show of support following the passage of the U.S. funding bill.
